title: Junior Preseason All State - Fourth Team
text:
Junior Preseason All State - Fourth Team Luke Feddersen IowaPreps.com Editor 
One of the most popular features on Iowa Preps is our preseason All State basketball teams. We take an in-depth look at Class of 2017 and name our fourth team junior All State team. See which of the elite athletes around Iowa made the cut as we take a look towards a winter full of hoops! 
Junior Preseason All State - Fourth Team Alex Martens, Midland, Wyoming
